casebody.data:
Daisy STEWART, Personal Representative of the Estate of Teodorico Q. Gomez, Ma-Doloria A. Gomez, and Ted D. Gomez, Plaintiffs-Appellants,
and
Empower PT and Fitness, Intervening Plaintiff,
v.
Ronel Raad HANA, Raad S. Hana, and Michael Jeffrey Yax, Defendants,
and
Farm Bureau General Insurance Company of Michigan, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 159728
COA: 341812 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 10, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the May 7, 2019 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.

Bernstein, J., did not participate because he has a family member with an interest that could be affected by the proceeding.
